title: 'more unfortuante language : "third" means 5 and "fifth" means 3.'
pid: ee55f234-fb0f-429f-8bc6-932e08be6477
body: |2-
  In a bizarre twist of fate,
  "major third" is our unfortunate name for
  the 12-edo interval that best approximates 5/4,
  and "perfect fifth" is the interval that best approximates 3/2.
